{
  "text": "Furthermore, recent measurements [CITATION_1] have shown that Mainline DHT's response time is consistently low, which makes it suitable for latency-sensitive applications such as on-demand video streaming.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "8585665"
